    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"prouder-than-all\">Prouder Than All</h3><p>The Leone Clan members carry themselves high with their orgins steming from the Land of Jungles. Members of this clan uses a speical transformation gifted to their bloodline by a sage beast long ago to overpower their opponents with nothing but their bear hands.</p><h4 id=\"leone-traits\">Leone Traits</h4><p><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Dex or Str, +1 Con or Wis <br /><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 35 feet. <br /><strong>Skill Proficiency:</strong> Acrobatics or Athletics, Martial Arts <br /><strong>Darkvision:</strong> You have Darkvision up to 30 feet.<br /><strong>Taijutsu Literacy:</strong> Your Taijutsu ability score is counted as being +2 higher, for the purpose of casting jutsu Higher Ranked jutsu with the Taijutsu Keyword through any Ability score Restrictions.</p>",
